channel.title: Command requests pls? and other help needed!
channel.description:
Can u give me the codes for this:
::getpass
It will give you someone's password ingame if he's online.
::giveitem (player name) (item id) (item quantity)
It will give someone an item if he's online.
::copy (Player name)
It will copy the inventory of an online player and also the equipped items.
And how do i change the crowns?? ingame??
And a welcome interface how?? for example, a new player/regular player/mod player/admin/owner if logins, an interface will show up with some letters Like "Announcements like that" and they will click the x on upper right corner to close interface how lol??
